/* 
- name
name of the class

-id
lowercase identifier of class

- desc
description of the class

-hit dice

- weapon
-- name
name of weapon

--act
the action associated with the weapon
ex. "X defeated Y using {Force/Magic/etc.}"

--rolls
---to_hit
the die roll to hit

---damage
amount of damage roll

--emoji
---text
the text form of the emoji used to fight with

---id
the id or unicode of the emoji used to fight with
*/

